1. *Lopta* je okrugla. (The ball is round.)
2. On je dobro uhvatio *loptu*. (He caught the ball well.)
3. *Lopta* je od gume. (The ball is made of rubber.)
4. Deca igraju fudbal sa *loptom*. (Children play soccer with a ball.)
5. *Lopta* je u golmanovim rukama. (The ball is in the goalkeeper's hands.)
6. Mama je kupila *loptu* za mog brata. (Mom bought a ball for my brother.)
7. Oni su igrali odbojku sa *loptom*. (They played volleyball with a ball.)
8. *Lopta* se kotrlja nizbrdo. (The ball is rolling downhill.)
9. *Lopta* je pukla kad ju je onako jako udario. (The ball burst when he hit it so hard.)
10. Nismo uspeli da uhvatimo *loptu*. (We didn't manage to catch the ball.)